As a young child, every year I'd be asked to sign birthday cards to a mysterious elderly aunt who lived far away.

00:12:41.840 --> 00:12:46.240
I never met her, never spoke to her, never saw any photos,

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:48.980
never got any cards in return,

00:12:48.980 --> 00:12:49.940
nothing.

